<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA624_07_IH_0004</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_07.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_07_ih_0004">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="4_deep_green" lang="y">
					3000원짜리 과자를 사는 데 이준이와 동생이 돈을 7 : 3으로 나누어 내려고 합니다. 두 사람은 각각 얼마씩
					내야 하는지 구해 보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
					<div class="img_area">
						<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_07_IH/0004_01_bg.png" alt="" />
						<div class="text_area">
							<p class="name" lang="y">이준</p>
							<div class="input_area">
								3000×
								<div class="fraction_box">
									<span>
										<span class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
											<math-field data-answer-single="7" class="w_80"></math-field>
										</span>
									</span>
									<span>
										<span class="input_wrap">
											<math-field data-answer-single="10" class="w_80"></math-field>
										</span>
									</span>
								</div>
								=<span class="input_wrap">
									<math-field data-answer-single="2100"></math-field>
								</span>
								<span lang="y">(원)</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="img_area">
						<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_07_IH/0004_02_bg.png" alt="" />
						<div class="text_area">
							<p class="name" lang="y">동생</p>
							<div class="input_area">
								3000×
								<div class="fraction_box">
									<span>
										<span class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
											<math-field data-answer-single="3" class="w_80"></math-field>
										</span>
									</span>
									<span>
										<span class="input_wrap">
											<math-field data-answer-single="10" class="w_80"></math-field>
										</span>
									</span>
								</div>
								=<span class="input_wrap">
									<math-field data-answer-single="900"></math-field>
								</span>
								<span lang="y">(원)</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p>3000원을 7:3으로 나눕니다.</p>
								<p class="in_flex align_center">
									이준: 3000×<span class="fraction_box"> <span>7</span><span>7+3</span></span
									>=3000×<span class="fraction_box"><span>7</span><span>10</span> </span>=2100(원)
								</p>
								<br />
								<p class="in_flex align_center mt_15">
									동생: 3000×<span class="fraction_box"> <span>3</span><span>7+3</span></span
									>=3000×<span class="fraction_box"> <span>3</span><span>10</span> </span>=900(원)
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
